将时间T分成长为
\begin_inset Formula $\delta t=T/N$
\end_inset

的
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

段，上面的表达式可以写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bra{q_{f}}\exp\left(-iHt\right)\ket{q_{i}}=\bra{q_{f}}\exp\left(-iH\delta t\right)\cdots\exp\left(-iH\delta t\right)\ket{q_{i}}
\]

\end_inset


